OL,3,C'Diversity is a strength': Sir Sadiq
OL,4,Creacts to Laila Cunningham's burka
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FSir Sadiq Khan said he "wouldn't
OL,8,Fdream" of telling women what to wear
OL,9,Fafter Reform UK's Laila Cunningham
OL,10,Findicated she would ban burkas if she
OL,11,Fbecomes Mayor of London.
OL,13,FResponding to one of Ms Cunningham's
OL,14,Fproposals since she was unveiled as
OL,15,FReform UK's mayoral candidate last
OL,16,Fweek, Sir Sadiq said "the idea you can
OL,17,Fstop and search somebody because of
OL,18,Fthe clothes they wear, all Londoners
OL,19,Fwould find it offensive."
