OL,3,C'Diversity is a strength': Sir Sadiq
OL,4,Creacts to Laila Cunningham's burka
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FThe Westminster councillor told The
OL,8,FTelegraph that she would "give orders
OL,9,Fto the police that any face coverings
OL,10,Fare a reason for stop and search",
OL,11,Fadding "you shouldn't cover your face".
OL,13,FReferring to the hijab, Ms Cunningham,
OL,14,Fwho is herself a Muslim, said: "That's
OL,15,Fnot religion. There's nowhere in the
OL,16,FKoran that says you have to cover your
OL,17,Fface or cover your hair. It says you
OL,18,Fhave to be modest.
