OL,3,C'Diversity is a strength': Sir Sadiq
OL,4,Creacts to Laila Cunningham's burka
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FWhen asked what he made of Ms
OL,8,FCunningham's comments, Sir Sadiq told
OL,9,FITV News London: "I would never dream
OL,10,Fof telling a woman how to dress, nor
OL,11,Fwould I think that's a reason.
OL,13,F"To arrest them or charge them with
OL,14,Fanything, I think it's really
OL,15,Fimportant to recognise that we have
OL,16,Fpeople in our city who are Jewish, who
OL,17,Fare Christian, who are Hindu, who are
OL,18,FMuslim, who are Buddhists, who are
OL,19,FSikh, who are members of organized
OL,20,Ffaith, and those that aren't.
