OL,3,C'Diversity is a strength': Sir Sadiq
OL,4,Creacts to Laila Cunningham's burka
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,F"The idea you can stop and search
OL,8,Fsomebody because of the clothes they
OL,9,Fwear, of their God worship, I think
OL,10,Fall English people, all decent English
OL,11,Fpeople, all British people, all
OL,12,FLondoners would find it offensive."
OL,14,F"What I will say is one of the joys
OL,15,Fabout London is our diversity. For me
OL,16,Fit's a strength and not a weakness,"
OL,17,Fhe added.
