OL,3,C'Diversity is a strength': Sir Sadiq
OL,4,Creacts to Laila Cunningham's burka
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FMs Cunningham, a former criminal
OL,8,Fprosecutor, promised an "all-out war
OL,9,Fon crime" if she wins when the capital
OL,10,Fnext goes to the polls in 2028, with
OL,11,F"new marching orders" for the
OL,12,FMetropolitan Police to "tackle crime
OL,13,Fthat matters".
OL,15,FReform UK's head of policy Zia Yusuf
OL,16,Fbriefly resigned from the party in
OL,17,FJune last year after describing Reform
OL,18,FMP Sarah Pochin's question to the
OL,19,FPrime Minister concerning a ban on
OL,20,Fburkas as "dumb".
