OL,3,C'Diversity is a strength': Sir Sadiq
OL,4,Creacts to Laila Cunningham's burka
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FReturning to the party just 48 hours
OL,8,Flater, Mr Yusuf said he made the
OL,9,Fcomments in "error", adding: "If there
OL,10,Fwere a vote and I was in Parliament, I
OL,11,Fwould probably vote to ban it (the
OL,12,Fburka)."
OL,14,FIn October last year, shadow justice
OL,15,Fsecretary Robert Jenrick said there is
OL,16,F"a strong argument" for preventing
OL,17,Fwomen from wearing the burka and that
OL,18,Fhe would "probably" ban it.
