OL,3,C'Diversity is a strength': Sir Sadiq
OL,4,Creacts to Laila Cunningham's burka
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FResponding to Mr Jenrick's comments, a
OL,8,Fspokesperson for the Prime Minister
OL,9,Fsaid: "Everyone has the legal right to
OL,10,Ffreedom of religion and this includes
OL,11,Fthe right to wear religious attire
OL,12,Fexcept where limitations are
OL,13,Fproscribed by law for specific limited
OL,14,Fpurposes."
